channel.title: Help running downloads!
channel.description:
I need help running downloads, i have been playing moparscape for a long while i am an admin on a few serv's and a mod on another and i am having trouble running any downloads i get of Moparscape. heres what happens, have WinRAR and all that stuff but when i went to click on runserv.bat i little command box popped up infront of me and said "java could not open file, press any botton to continue" this has never happened before and i am upset cause i have spent like 30 hours downloading serv's :confused:
Also when i try to go on a serv on moparscape v.2 client it says please start server or server must be down when i know it isnt casue i use server status list half the time... :mad:
